HYROX is finally in India and I’m training for it at @otfworli !!! It is a fitness race that mixes running with workouts like sled pushes, burpees, and rowing 💥 Think if 10k and CrossFit had a competitive and structured baby! I think it’s going to be more of a mental game, esp since im not a runner so can’t wait to find out 🙌🏻
If you’re in the HYROX crew, drop a 👋 — let’s connect and suffer together! #HYROXTraining #FunctionalFitness #RaceReady #HyroxFam #ﬁtnessmotivation #workoutmotivation
